<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #007AFF;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #007AFF;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background-color: #007AFF;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #0051D5;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #E3F2FD;
      border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>🔔 Remindly</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <h2>You've Been Invited to Help!</h2>
    
    <p>Hello!</p>
    
    <p><strong><%= @inviter.display_name %></strong> has invited you to help care for <strong><%= @senior.display_name %></strong> on Remindly.</p>
    
    <div class="info-box">
      <strong>📋 What you can do:</strong>
      <ul style="margin: 10px 0;">
        <li>View and manage tasks for <%= @senior.display_name %></li>
        <li>See reminders and schedules</li>
        <li>Track activity and care coordination</li>
        <li>Collaborate with other caregivers</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <p>Click the button below to sign in and get started:</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= @login_url %>" class="button">Sign In to Remindly</a>
    </div>
    
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
      If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
      <code style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 5px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;"><%= @login_url %></code>
    </p>
    
    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      <strong>Your account:</strong> <%= @caregiver.email %>
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>
      This email was sent by Remindly<br>
      Your Personal Reminder Assistant
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
